my work is so funny.&nbsp;
i sit all day long and just draw pictures on post-its secretly, and think about why anyone would want to live in a place called 'enclave' or 'village ville'
everyone who calls here&nbsp;is named steve and sometimes this is the capital of bitch city

and when i told them i didn't eat meat it wasn't pretty at all.&nbsp;
just for some lousy samples of quik-brik&nbsp;

i'm leaving for muncie in 54 short minutes.&nbsp;yeah chile! it won't be the same as it was from a hot pot with heart shaped corn bread, but it will be delicious.
